The hero wakes up in a mysterious, enchanted land with no memory of their past,He feels thirsty and goes to nearby riverstream to quench
his thirst , suddenly he noticed that his reflection in water is shown as a warrior. While he is still puzzled about the reflection,
some sentences start to appear in the riverstream. It says - " The warrior's quest: Crystal ball, remember, Nature is way". 
He takes responsibility , but did'nt know where to start. He remembers the sentence and follows the direction of a star.
